A modern terminal interface floating in a dark, abstract digital space. The terminal window displays colorful command-line code with syntax highlighting (green, blue, purple text on dark background). Multiple terminal windows are layered at slight angles, creating depth. Subtle glowing effects and particles emanate from the terminals, suggesting power and productivity. The overall mood is futuristic and professional, with a dark theme (deep navy/black background) and vibrant neon accent colors. No text or logos. Cinematic lighting with volumetric glow effects.